The LWFA simulations were carried out for various a0 values, corresponding to the laser intensity I0 = 2EL/τ0.5/πw02, achievable by focusing the G beam to a spot area equal to πw02/2. The corresponding electric field of the laser pulse was recalculated as,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
